rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0001
rows.name:
If you wanna know about Gulan bugs,
ask me!

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0002
rows.name: Which insect should we ask about?

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0007
rows.name: You can catch those anywhere in Gula.

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0008
rows.name:
That's common knowledge, isn't it?
Don't ask me such obvious questions.

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0009
rows.name:
Huh?
Umm, does that even exist?

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0010
rows.name:
I've never caught one in Gula...
Does it really exist? Is this a trick question?

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0011
rows.name:
But I can't say for sure it doesn't exist...
I need to study more...

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0013
rows.name:
You can catch them in the area from
Hermit's Hollow to Coolley Lake!

rows.label: tlk41100221_02_msg0014
rows.name:
See?
I know my stuff, right?
